Minister of Culture, Sports and Tourism Do Jong-hwan and South Korea's 
National Olympic Committee President Lee Kee-heung join their hands as 
they pose during a signing ceremony at the Olympic Museum on January 20,
 2018 in Lausanne. North Korea will send 22 athletes to the Winter Games
 in the South. The two nations will also march together at the opening 
